{"title":"在VSCode中为VueCLI创建的项目选择代码格式化工具","date":"2021-06-14T11:56:53.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月14日","L":"2021/06/14","MM-DD":"06-14"},"link":"post/2021/202106/在VSCode中为VueCLI创建的项目选择代码格式化工具","tags":["vscode"],"updated":"2022-01-31T22:41:53.300Z","content":"<p><img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/xjQWFnn.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"vue-cli几种格式化方案创建项目的区别\">vue cli几种格式化方案创建项目的区别<a title=\"#vue-cli几种格式化方案创建项目的区别\" href=\"#vue-cli几种格式化方案创建项目的区别\"></a></h2>\n<p>选择不同的选项 会生成不同的 eslint配置  和 不同格式的代码<br>\n在vscode当中  通过  formatOnSave 在保存代码的时候调用格式化器<br>\n如果格式化器 格式化的结果和  当初选择的配置不同结果就会报错</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/obI7q2L.png\" alt=\"error prevent\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/iuNL6hw.png\" alt=\"airbnb\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/OcDOop2.png\" alt=\"标准\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/3jS39ID.png\" alt=\"prettier\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>刚刚生成的代码是肯定能通过eslint检查的 一旦通过vscode进行格式化之后就不一定能通过检查了</p>\n<p>目前我已经知道的vue 文件代码格式化器 有3个</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/IpQv3RW.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>其中vetur 和  prettier 其实是同一个, 可以很好的格式化 (eslint+prettier) 项目<br>\nvetur 默认调用了 prettier,当然可以手动更改</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/vAGf5WM.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;vetur.format.defaultFormatter.html&quot;</span>: <span class=\"string\">&quot;js-beautify-html&quot;</span>, </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//格式化.vue中html</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;vetur.format.defaultFormatter.js&quot;</span>: <span class=\"string\">&quot;vscode-typescript&quot;</span>, </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//让vue中的js按编辑器自带的ts格式进行格式化</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>volar 是另外一个  这个格式化工具<br>\n可以很好的格式化 (eslint+standard config) 和 (eslint+airbnb config )的项目</p>\n<p>至于 (eslint with error prevention only) 项目 要求比较宽松 应该是几个格式化器都能够使用</p>\n<h2 id=\"vue-cli-创建项目几种格式化方案的蛋疼点\">vue cli 创建项目几种格式化方案的蛋疼点<a title=\"#vue-cli-创建项目几种格式化方案的蛋疼点\" href=\"#vue-cli-创建项目几种格式化方案的蛋疼点\"></a></h2>\n<p>eslint+standard config</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> router = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> VueRouter(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">mode</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;history&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">base</span>: process.env.BASE_URL,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  routes</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 强制单引号, routes后面不允许有逗号, 最后一个小括号后面不允许有分号, 看起来有点蛋疼</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>eslint+prettier</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">    <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https://github.com/vuejs/vue-cli/tree/dev/packages/%40vue/cli-plugin-router&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">    <span class=\"attr\">target</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;_blank&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">    <span class=\"attr\">rel</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;noopener&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">  &gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    router</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">// <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span>的所有属性必须分行显示, 太鸡儿蛋疼了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>eslint+airbnb<br>\n感觉就 airbnb的方案还算靠谱点</p>\n","prev":{"title":"VSCode插件prettier-vscode使用说明","link":"post/2021/202106/VSCode插件-prettier-vscode-使用说明"},"next":{"title":"VSCode 控制Markdown文件软换行","link":"post/2021/202106/VSCode-控制Markdown文件软换行"},"plink":"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202106/在VSCode中为VueCLI创建的项目选择代码格式化工具/","toc":[{"id":"vue-cli几种格式化方案创建项目的区别","title":"vue cli几种格式化方案创建项目的区别","index":"1"},{"id":"vue-cli-创建项目几种格式化方案的蛋疼点","title":"vue cli 创建项目几种格式化方案的蛋疼点","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"李攀攀","link":"<a href=\"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202106/在VSCode中为VueCLI创建的项目选择代码格式化工具/\" title=\"在VSCode中为VueCLI创建的项目选择代码格式化工具\">http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202106/在VSCode中为VueCLI创建的项目选择代码格式化工具/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"},"reading_time":"520 字约 3 分钟"}